The prefix arg TODO-ONLY limits the search to TODO entries.

\(fn &optional TODO-ONLY MATCH)" t nil)
(autoload 'org-agenda-list-stuck-projects "~/.emacs.d/.local/straight/build/org/org-agenda" "\
